<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <style type="text/CSS">
  body {
    background-image: url(/assets/indeximage2.jpg);
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
    background-size: 100%;
    z-index: 0px;
    background-color: #EAE7E5;
    color: black;
    background-position: center 94px;
  }

  .col-md-8{
    text-align: center;
    height: 100%;
    color: #EAE7E5;
  }

  .row.features {
    margin-top: 200px;
    color: #40353D;
    text-align: center;
  }


  </style>

</head>
<body>

  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-8">
      <div class="text">
          <h1>Welcome to Heed the Herd!</h1>
      <h3>Making sure your horses don't die <br>since 2015!</h3>
      </div>
            <% if user_signed_in? %>
          <%= link_to "Sign Out", destroy_user_session_path, class: "btn btn-default", method: :delete %>
        <% else %>
          <%= link_to "Sign up", new_user_registration_path, class: "btn btn-default"%> 
          <%= link_to "Sign in", new_user_session_path, class: "btn btn-default"%>
        <% end %>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4"> </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row features">
    <div class="col-md-4"><i class="fa fa-tint fa-3x"></i><br><b> Rain alerts</b><br><br> Sends email reminders to blanket your horses if there will be rain in your area.
     </div>
    <div class="col-md-4"><i class="fa fa-bell fa-3x"></i><br> <b>Appointment reminder</b><br><br> Receive an email reminder one week before any routine care is needed.</div>
    <div class="col-md-4"><i class="fa fa-line-chart fa-3x"></i><br><b> Weight chart</b><br> <br>Track your horses weight to ensure that they remain healthy. </div>
  </div>

</body>
</html>

